{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/extras/LOGO_ope.png?t=1739768472\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Details</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00d4pe is a 3D platforming game in which you play as a little hero named B\u00f4. His quest will lead him through enchanted forest and temples where he\u2019ll need to deliver shamans from corruption before the sun sets forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/extras/OpeAvatar.png?t=1739768472\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game has 10 playable levels in which you\u2019ll discover forest and temple environments. Forets are more 3D-platforming-oriented and the temples are puzzle-oriented. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the adventure, you\u2019ll learn many skills to help you during your quest such as dashing through walls, push rocks, double-jump and even transform your character in a little sphere to access new opportunities. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Production</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This original title was developed in 15 weeks by the class of 2018-2019 of Campus ADN, a public video game college in downtown Montreal, Quebec, Canada. The students worked in two teams to make the games Blank and \u00d4pe. Each game was created by about 30 students in total from Animation, Level Design and Modeling programs during their third semester under the supervision of professionals from the industry. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/extras/Cover_Art_\u00d4pe.png?t=1739768472\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739768472","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/page.bg.jpg?t=1739768472","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739768472","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739768472","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170200/extras/LOGO_ope.png?t=1739768472\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Details</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00d4pe is a 3D platforming game in which you play as a little hero named B\u00f4. His quest will lead him through enchanted forest and temples where he\u2019ll need to deliver sha